><br />\n以前d基層 打返牛工返十幾個鐘 一放假就無所事事 唔似我地咁多嗜好 所以退左休咪係街發呆囉 廢中廢老咪就係咁黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學佢地邏輯囉<br />\n佢地成日話自已後生冇人幫佢，點解而家後生要人幫<br />\n<br />\n而家咪，佢地後生果時d廢老都冇人幫，點解佢地老左要人幫"},{"pid":"7ddff7178c51b4d685bba68b20298ebdfcad5b4d","tid":210213,"uid":18167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢老令治安更差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廢老好鐘意將自已缺點講成優點，後生優點講成缺點<br />\n佢地一定覺得自已偷到野好醒，店員好蠢"},{"pid":"6de34ff0ea1839a45a82a57e130c878fb488ba91","tid":210213,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:04:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f61b4dc2959b23faf5702b988ad1c1b72e3a6f5","tid":210213,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:05:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32a816334338385bccce5948cf8b106d52611f16","tid":210213,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:06:34.000Z","msg":"點撚樣睇都唔撚係無得食既問題"},{"pid":"3d760729a653c77070b90bd0c88357bf53eb1a8b","tid":210213,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:06:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">膽子大的老人，吃不飽就會去偷，更多膽子小的老人，只能透過行乞或者捱餓去度過每一天，政府推出的年金計畫跟他們一點關係都沒有，他們身上幾十塊錢都沒有，何來資格有一百萬去投資年金。</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地將來老咗會唔會係咁</blockquote><br />\n以前d基層 打返牛工返十幾個鐘 一放假就無所事事 唔似我地咁多嗜好 所以退左休咪係街發呆囉 廢中廢老咪就係咁黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日日朝早咪遊車河，係街鳩行鳩企"},{"pid":"e93965a09cce1e7780dca90bba0b5f8aa8691926","tid":210213,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食二手飯 真係社會有責任</blockquote><br />\n前世欠撚左佢呀 有咩責任？</blockquote><br />\n佢自己年輕時唔努力係我地既責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點證明佢年輕冇努力？</blockquote><br />\n有努力會搞成咁？</blockquote><br />\n努力同付出成正比？<br />\n努力就唔會搞成咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前咩環境 依家咩環境"}]}